Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:38.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When all are sheltering within,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:42.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,there comes an imitation of spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:46.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Linger in bliss for too long
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:50.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and your flesh will soon be frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:57.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:04.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a butterfly.
