Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:04.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got caught in the snow. Do you\Nmind if I spend the night here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:22.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:27.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, where'd he wander off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:14.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should teach him not to touch weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:19.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that was a rare one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did it again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:30.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,can you see those things he's seeing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We call them Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:43.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are those who fear them and those who like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems he's quite the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:52.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's always liked animals. He'd catch\Nthem and bring them home all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, ever since he\Nbegan to see those things,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's been doing the strangest things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:05.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That winter, he disappeared in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:09.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a blizzard for the next few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've done all we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had lost all hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:28.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wandered back home in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:33.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since, he'd run after the strange\Nthings he insisted he saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:40.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time we were about to run out of food\Nfor the winter, he'd just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:45.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd find him passed out at the outskirts of the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:49.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he'd sleep all the way until spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he'd always have with him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:59.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,a bag of fruits and vegetables that don't\Nnormally grow during the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I ask him where he'd been –
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:12.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't open the bag outside. It'll\Nbe a pain if people find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all he'd ever say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:21.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of us live alone, so I can understand\Nthat he's trying to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:26.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I just can't get it off of my mind.\NIt just doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:32.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That might be a "Harumagai".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Harumagai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's said that there's a Mushi called Usobuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,that has the appearance of a flower blooming on a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,that has the appearance of a flower blooming on a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:48.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It emits a special stimulating scent to animate\Nhibernating plants and animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:52.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then it consumes the energy\Nof the animals that it attracts,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:56.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,causing them to continue sleeping until spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all I know about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:04.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what exactly are Mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not all of them are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:12.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're usually harmless as long\Nas you don't mess with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:19.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could teach him which ones to watch out for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, Miharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:30.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That one over there. That one's not so safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:33.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, see, there's tons of them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't bring them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Settle down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it, I shouldn't have made that offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:48.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, where do you find those vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to steal them from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take me there, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to tell my sister, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:02.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just want to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know you've got your\Nsister worried, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you at least tell her where you get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then she'd come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can understand you wanting to be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:24.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you think you're just being selfish if\Nyou don't think about how your sister feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got a place to go home to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't stray too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:44.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? How 'bout these ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:51.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miharu, you better take it seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:59.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko-san, could you please continue tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:04.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine with me. I don't have any other plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long can you stay then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:14.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder... it depends on the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:19.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I think I could stay until\Nhe learns most of the Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a fast learner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe ten more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Depends on the area?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a tendency to attract Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:35.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't stay too long in places where\Nthere are too many Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't good to have too many of them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:43.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the types of Mushi that Miharu\Nis finding, it's probably not that rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could probably stay for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can stay for as long as you can then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:55.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard traveling in the winter, isn't it?\NYou should stay 'til spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:59.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... it'll depend on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A cocoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:22.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was around there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looked like a Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are they gathering in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:37.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thought so; there's more than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:46.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might have stayed for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko, I have some errands to run in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take care of Miharu, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's sleeping inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:15.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn kid, wandering off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How far did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit, where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:56.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should go home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miharu! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could he have...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:28.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Harumagai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:40.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Suzu, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same as always, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll be awake by spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:55.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to stay until then, but I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:59.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... Miharu's going to be sad when he wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll come visit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:25.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When all calls for an awakening,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the imitation lays to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And someone in the winter mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:47.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,pretends that it's spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Suzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:15.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been asleep for a whole year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:22.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:30.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to find out where Miharu was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:34.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you might end up like Miharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:37.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was supposed to wake up by spring, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something he needs to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should know what that is, if I go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:47.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I don't come back, search for\Nme north of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:09.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miharu's footsteps went this way last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was in Miharu's bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Smells sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:46.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:22.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to leave quickly. "Usobuki" look\Nlike flowers on trees, as I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They all look like normal flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:35.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need some hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's losing its body heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The air smells different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:21.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are those butterflies...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally figured it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:44.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I'm falling asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:19.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:23.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:30.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'll wake them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,just come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's already spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Miharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:53.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:54.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:17.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the flower-like thing on the roof emitted\Na strong aroma for the next few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and changed into a familiar form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:25.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought the thing I saw\Nback then was an "Usobuki".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:31.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you were using the Usobuki's metamorphosis\Nto signal the Harumagai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:32.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:38.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't let it out, it would have become\Na butterfly by springtime and woken me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should have told me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:46.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to keep it secret, because I like them the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:51.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They give us food during the winter,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:55.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and they look really pretty flying around in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:21:01.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they're just doing their thing,\Ngathering food to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:07.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? I see you're getting the hang of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:11.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, they're in no way your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're just an odd neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get too friendly with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:21.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though, you can like them if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:31.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you stop by at my place first?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:35.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I've stayed here too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should leave as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:42.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister's gonna be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:46.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell her I said "thanks".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:54.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you'll come again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:00.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows, well, not during the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:07.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,People are weak during the winter too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:17.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phantom springs blooming on frozen mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:21.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Homes illuminated along snowy paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such are the allure of long stays.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:32.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Animals, insects and people alike.
